metadata.name: INNER VOICE
metadata.description:
Inner voice is all about tuning into the magic that following your intuition can bring. Madame Love chooses to follow a pathway even when she cannot see the road, as she feels a pull so strong that she must walk it anyway. 

Flamingos are beautiful symbology for balance, love and playfulness. They stand on one leg with grace and poise and act as masters, skilled to train us to find the balance we seek. 

Walking an unclear path can require us to maintain that balance so we are ready for the opportunities that present themselves, have an open heart and mind so we can recognize the right doors to walk through as they open up and be walking the path that encompasses compassion and self love so that our decisions are being guided by what will truly make us fulfilled. 

Join Madame Love, and find your Inner Voice that will take you to the heights that your soul dreams of.
